Package pw.ollie.politics.universe

Class Universe

  • java.lang.Object
    • pw.ollie.politics.universe.Universe
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Storable
    public final class Universe
extends Object
implements Storable
    A Universe is a collection of PoliticsWorlds which are subject to a particular set of UniverseRules and share existing GroupLevels and Citizen data.
